{"title": "Considerations on Representative Government", "description": "Mill's volume was published in 1861 as an argument favoring this form of governance. Mill covers what forms of government work best, including when representative government is applicable and when not. He details appropriate functions of representative bodies and warns of problems to avoid. He distinguishes between true and false democracy. Other areas covered include how voting is carried out, the role of a second chamber in Parliament, and how an executive branch might function. (Summary by Bill Boerst)", "duration": 35686, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "2881", "name": "John Stuart Mill"}], "coverArt": "http://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt29/considerations_1303.jpg", "copyright_year": "1861", "genres": ["Political Science"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Bill Boerst"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Bill Boerst"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "J. M. Smallheer"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Dawn Larsen"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "00 - Preface", "readers": [4788], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/representativegovernment_1302_librivox/representativegovernment_00_mill_64kb.mp3", "duration": 122}, {"section": 1, "title": "01 - Chapter 1A", "readers": [4788], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/representativegovernment_1302_librivox/representativegovernment_01_mill_64kb.mp3", "duration": 805}, {"section": 2, "title": "02 - Chapter 1B", "readers": [4788], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/representativegovernment_1302_librivox/representativegovernment_02_mill_64kb.mp3", "duration": 864}, {"section": 3, "title": "03 - Chapter 2A", "readers": [4788], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/representativegovernment_1302_librivox/representativegovernment_03_mill_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1408}, {"section": 4, "title": "04 - Chapter 2B", "readers": [4788], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/representativegov